data.description: This impressive living space features 4 bedrooms (could easily be 5) and 2.5 bathrooms. The open floor plan boasts expansive living areas with a flow through living and dining area. The generously sized backyard and deck offer an excellent location for summer gatherings. The covered patio beneath allows you to enjoy the outdoors even in less favorable conditions. Spend the winter months tinkering in the attached garage or in the 2nd living room curled up next to the wood fireplace. Don't miss the opportunity to finish this house and make it your home! Call Tiffany Ross at 406-799-4423 or your real estate professional to schedule a showing.
